<h2 class="bold font-l">Feodora Saves Miya</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When a young girl nearly falls to her death, Feodora, a young witch, saves her. But she lives in a world where humans detest monsters, witches included, so instead of thanking her for saving one of their own, they call her a monster and kick her out of the village. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/UngratefulBastard" class='trope-example-link'>Ungrateful Bastard</a></p>
</div>
